data.meta_description: Download this stock image: British number one tennis player, Tim Henman (left), plays against Joe Salisbury, 11, joint British number one in his age group, during the launch of the Esporta Raquets Academy in Chiswick, west London. The Academy is the first of 18, which are to open nation-wide with the aim of encouraging tennis playing talent in children, including among non-club members. - G6H112 from Alamy's library of millions of high resolution stock photos, illustrations and vectors.
